OL,3,C'I'll never stop being angry': Cat
OL,4,Cowner's warning after pet shot in the
OL,5,Cface
OL,7,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's full report by
OL,8,FMel Bloor
OL,10,FA cat owner from Hampshire is warning
OL,11,Fhis community to be vigilant after his
OL,12,Fpet was deliberately targeted and shot
OL,13,Fin the face with a catapult.
OL,15,FHazel, an 18-month-old tabby from
OL,16,FYateley, has been forced to have her
OL,17,Feye removed following the attack,
OL,18,Fwhich occurred last month near Lawford
OL,19,FCrescent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
