OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773245482
OL,3,C'I'll never stop being angry': Cat
OL,4,Cowner's warning after pet shot in the
OL,5,Cface
OL,7,FHer owner, Neville Imray, believes the
OL,8,Fattack was a deliberate act of cruelty
OL,9,Fand fears that other pets or even
OL,10,Fpeople could be next.
OL,12,FThe incident happened on Wednesday,
OL,13,F19th February, during Hazel's usual
OL,14,Fevening routine.
OL,16,F"I fed her normally at 5pm," Mr. Imray
OL,17,Fsaid. "She usually goes out in the
OL,18,Fgarden after that; we let her roam
OL,19,Ffreely. I was in the study and my wife
OL,20,Fwas in the living room.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773245482
OL,3,C'I'll never stop being angry': Cat
OL,4,Cowner's warning after pet shot in the
OL,5,Cface
OL,7,F"The cat came in about six. She was
OL,8,Fbleeding a lot, but she was very calm.
OL,9,FI suppose she was in quite a lot of
OL,10,Fpain."
OL,12,FHazel was rushed to an out-of-hours
OL,13,Fvet where X-rays revealed a high-
OL,14,Fvelocity projectile lodged in her head.
OL,16,F"The vet phoned to say that the cat
OL,17,Fhad in fact been shot. They needed my
OL,18,Fpermission to operate. Every time I
OL,19,Flook at the cat, what's happened is
OL,20,Fquite obvious. I don't think I'll ever
OL,21,Fstop being angry."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773245482
OL,3,C'I'll never stop being angry': Cat
OL,4,Cowner's warning after pet shot in the
OL,5,Cface
OL,7,FWhile Hazel is now recovering at home
OL,8,Fand adapting to life with one eye, the
OL,9,Femotional toll on the family remains
OL,10,Fhigh.
OL,12,FLocal residents and the Town Council
OL,13,Fsay this is not an isolated incident.
OL,15,FIn recent months, several reports have
OL,16,Femerged of wildlife being targeted in
OL,17,Fthe area, including ducks, swans, and
OL,18,Fa heron.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
